data.description: Compact and mighty! So much good stuff offered - Large main floor bedroom w/full bath, large kitchen with all appliances, large countertop area to dining room w/ceiling fan.  Great cubbies for books or games in living room. Lots of windows for added light.  Upstairs you'll find a loft area w/skylight at the top of stairs -makes a great reading/computer area- primary bedroom has a huge closet/storage area, .75 bath where a stackable washing and dryer fits, vaulted ceiling and private deck. Detached garage w/studio, .75 bath, deck and large closet.   Fully fenced yard with lots of sunlight for garden space, fruit trees or play equipment.  5 minutes to grocery store, 15 minutes to Port Townsend ferry, 40 minutes to Sequim or Poulsbo.
